@startuml
[*] --> Idle
Idle --> [*]
Idle --> HourMode : press hour button
HourMode --> MinuteMode : press minute button
MinuteMode --> AlarmHourMode : press alarm hour button
AlarmHourMode --> AlarmMinuteMode : press alarm minute button
AlarmMinuteMode --> HourMode : press hour button
HourMode --> IncreaseValue : press increase button
MinuteMode --> IncreaseValue : press increase button
AlarmHourMode --> IncreaseValue : press increase button
AlarmMinuteMode --> IncreaseValue : press increase button
IncreaseValue --> HourMode : increase value
IncreaseValue --> MinuteMode : increase value
IncreaseValue --> AlarmHourMode : increase value
IncreaseValue --> AlarmMinuteMode : increase value
Idle --> AlarmOn : press alarm on button
AlarmOn --> AlarmOff : press alarm off button
AlarmOff --> Idle : press alarm off button
Idle --> LightOn : press light on button
LightOn --> LightOff : press light off button
LightOff --> Idle : press light off button
AlarmOn --> Alarm : alarm time matches current time
Alarm --> AlarmOff : press stop alarm button
@enduml
